{"tid":1823858,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話影大頭有問題的同我入來！","createTime":"2020-01-14T04:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T04:59:09.000Z","uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15f920ca301bf6755cebd97253bff4eccc9b29f0","tid":1823858,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:22:49.000Z","msg":"From facebook friend :<br />\n<br />\n見到有人問搞總罷工點解o甘難。呢個問題之所以成為問題，系因為我地睇太多童話化消過毒的19歷史。歷史上的大罷工，如省港大罷工, 其實很多都係靠罷工組織強迫人唔返工，你敢返工就打9你甚至殺左你而達成的。美國其中一個罷工鬥爭最成功的工會teamster，系同意大利黑手黨一夥的。香港地，你擋吓地鐵畀人鬧吓就討論應唔應該阻人返工，真係收皮啦。<br />\n<br />\n人地西方國家罷工，最緊要系組糾察線（picket line），唔系和理非篤勇武灰，而系封廠唔畀人返工，你敢越過糾察線返工就打9你。<a href=\"https://money.howstuffworks.com/strike3.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.howstuffworks.com%2Fstrike3.htm&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHDFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=74e730c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.howstuffworks.com/strike3.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n說好的黃色經濟圈呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6945da934b4ea1576cd2d3607b521b7438a7d212","tid":1823858,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:29:34.000Z","msg":"又開post討論影大頭<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"fea4a796cb8e240832028504aba4920872941f54","tid":1823858,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T04:59:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪仲喺度討論呢單野"}]}